txt.en: You have encountered the villainous Corsair captain, Hamarsun. The vile man believes in being at the front line to see each death of the enemy first hand.
You have defeated Hamarsun and his warband.
A captain in the Corsair ranks, Hamarsun believes in being at the front line to see each death of the enemy first hand.
Hamarsun can be found patrolling Dor-en-Ernil.\n\nYou have encountered Hamarsun and should defeat him for the good of the people in Dor-en-Ernil.
You have slain Hamarsun and vanquished a threat to the safety of all that dwell within Dor-en-Ernil.
You have defeated Hamarsun and his warband!
